project.longname: Digital Archive of the Swiss Society for Folklore Studies (SSFS)

descriptions.de: Digitales Archiv der Schweizerischen Gesellschaft für Volkskunde (SGV), welches das Fotoarchiv und das Volksliedarchiv (VLA) umfasst.
descriptions.fr: Archive numérique de la Société suisse des traditions populaires (SSTP) qui comprend les archives photographique et les archives des chansons populaires.
descriptions.en: Digital Archive of the Swiss Society for Folklore Studies (SSFS), which contains the image and the folk song archives.
descriptions.it: Archivio digitale della Società Svizzera per le Tradizioni Popolari (SSTP), che contiene il database delle immagini e l'archivo delle canzoni poplari.

keywords: Participatory Knowledge Practices in Analogue and Digital Image Archives
